refentry.refsect1:
Description
??? bindParam String parameter-name var variable-name integer data-type integer length
&warn.experimental.func;
Binds a parameter to the specified variable name.
Execute a prepared statement with bound variables
/* Execute a prepared statement by binding PHP variables */ $calories = 150; $colour = 'red'; $sth = $dbh->prepare('SELECT name, colour, calories FROM fruit WHERE calories < ?' AND colour = ?); $sth->bindParam(1, $calories, PDO_PARAM_INT) $sth->bindParam(2, $colour, PDO_PARAM_STR, 12) $sth->execute();
